usage: route_humanize_scene.py [-h] [--heading HEADING] --text-file TEXT_FILE
                               [--scene {AUTO,COURSE,GENERAL,MODELING,RESEARCH}]
                               [--policy POLICY]

Route one complete Chinese writing unit to a Humanize scene.

options:
